<seg id="14">The special feature of & FSView; is to graphically display nested folder hierarchies using a so-called tree map. tree-Maps permit the representation of the size of objects in nested structures. each object is represented by a rectangle, whose surface is proportional to its size. this size must have the property that the sum of the sizes of the child objects is smaller or equal to the size of the object.</seg>
